    "And the importance weights of \"landing\", \"steps\", and \"handrail' which appear in \"candidate 5 (GT)\" are relatively high.",
    "As a result, the landmark prediction is successfully corrected to indicate the GT action.",
    "Landark shifting.",
    "Fig. 5 shows that our landmark shifting module takes better advantage of the landmark navigation order for landmark discovery.",
    "It can effectively mitigate the stuck and disordered landmark prediction caused by scene complexity."
